thread.title: No. 8 Hawaii holds off UC Irvine in volleyball
thread.title_full: No. 8 Hawaii holds off UC Irvine in volleyball - Hawaii News - Honolulu Star-Advertiser

author: Cindy Luis
title: No. 8 Hawaii holds off UC Irvine in volleyball
text:
Senior Tai Manu-Olevao put down 14 kills and No. 8 Hawaii won its 13th straight, defeating UC Irvine 25-17, 25-23, 21-25, 26-24, in a Big West volleyball match Saturday night at the Stan Sheriff Center. Emily Maglio added 12 kills, including the match-ender, for the Rainbow Wahine (18-1, 8-0 Big West).
Marisa Bubica led the Anteaters (8-11, 2-5) with 14 kills.
